<p>This guide provides both a relatively easy way to install MediaWiki on a Windows PC using the <a href="//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/XAMPP" class="extiw" title="w:XAMPP">XAMPP</a> stack, and step-by-step instructions for installing each of the separate programs first. Both methods have been tested on Windows XP SP 2, but only the XAMPP method has been tested on Windows Vista.</p>
<p></p>
<div id="toc" class="toc">
